column10: Crossing Street from middle school, stopped at 3 way stop sign intersection, no vehicles at intersection. Started to cross. Dark SUV sped through and did not stop, slow down, or pause.
Multiple vehicles ran stop signs while disabled pedestrian was waiting to cross.

Over 10 vehicles ran stop sign during 5min period. Two vehicles ran stop sign while a pedestrian was crossing, and swerved around them. All drivers were speeding in a residential area and a school zone.
Over 8 vehicles ran stop sign while pedestrian was at crosswalk waiting to cross.
